TopicTitle: V1.0 loads, but no parts available

If the download failed you'll need to verify the game cache to make it download any missing or damaged files, this should be standard procedure for anyone on Steam ![:)](//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif)

> 
> If the download failed you'll need to verify the game cache to make it download any missing or damaged files, this should be standard procedure for anyone on Steam ![:)](//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif)

That was it. I cleaned out the munged files, deleted the appcache, and DL'd it again. Everything shows up now. Lesson learned: Always clean out the old junk and kill the appcache before grabbing the freshest copy...
Woot, great, glad it worked BARCLONE ![:)](//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif)
